Located in the [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]] [[Naboo system/Legends|system]], '''Kylantha's Whim''' was a mostly deserted quadrant of [[Realspace/Legends|space]], usually safe for travel and [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]] jumps.

==History==
The [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] patrolled the region frequently. It was named after [[Monarch of Naboo/Legends|Queen]] [[Kylantha]], the successor to Queen [[Apailana/Legends|Apailana]]. At one point, a young and wealthy suitor, in an attempt to win her heart and hand in marriage, purchased the quadrant for her; however, Kylantha politely refused his offer, saying that she had "married" her people and wished to serve them with all of her time. Heartbroken, the suitor renamed the quadrant "Kylantha's Whim".

